com.guidewire.ab.webservices.entity

Class ContactFindMatchResult

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.guidewire.ab.webservices.entity.GWObject
      • com.guidewire.ab.webservices.entity.ContactFindMatchResult
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class ContactFindMatchResult
extends GWObject
implements java.io.Serializable
    Deprecated since ClaimCenter 8.0 along with the IAddressBookAdapter. This is a non-persistent entity that represents the results of definitive match search. Besides the matched Contact objects, it also contains a result type. See the ContactMatchResultType typelist for more detail about the result of the match.
